<section class="about-section">
    <div class="about">
        <p class="section-kicker" data-i18n data-en="Profile" data-es="Perfil">Profile</p>
        <h2 data-i18n data-en="Frontend engineering with product judgment" data-es="Ingenieria frontend con criterio de producto">Frontend engineering with product judgment</h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="signal" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="copy" data-i18n data-en="As a self-taught developer and entrepreneur, I have delivered complex projects successfully from planning through implementation. I find creative solutions to challenges, collaborate effectively with teams, and bring communication, leadership, punctuality, and strategic thinking to every delivery." data-es="Como autodidacta y emprendedor, he logrado realizar con exito una variedad de proyectos complejos, desde la planificacion hasta la implementacion. Soy capaz de encontrar soluciones creativas a los desafios y de trabajar eficazmente en equipo, utilizando mis habilidades de comunicacion y liderazgo. Ademas, mi compromiso con la puntualidad y mi vision estrategica me permiten siempre cumplir con los plazos y alcanzar resultados sobresalientes.">
                As a self-taught developer and entrepreneur, I have delivered complex projects successfully from planning through implementation. I find creative solutions to challenges, collaborate effectively with teams, and bring communication, leadership, punctuality, and strategic thinking to every delivery.
            </div>
            <div class="north-card">
                <strong data-i18n data-en="Focus" data-es="Enfoque">Focus</strong>
                <p data-i18n data-en="Clean interfaces, scalable systems, and thoughtful delivery from idea to production." data-es="Interfaces limpias, sistemas escalables y entregas cuidadas desde la idea hasta produccion.">Clean interfaces, scalable systems, and thoughtful delivery from idea to production.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style>
    .about-section {
        background: #fbfbf7;
        color: #102126;
        padding: 6rem 1.25rem 3rem;
    }
    .about {
        margin: auto;
		max-width: 1024px;
        width: 100%;
	}
    .section-kicker {
        color: var(--maple);
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.18em;
        margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h2 {
        color: #102126;
        font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 4.4rem);
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1;
        margin: 0 0 2rem;
        max-width: 12ch;
    }
    .about-grid {
        align-items: start;
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        grid-template-columns: 6rem minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(15rem, 0.44fr);
    }
    .signal {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--maple), #ffb703, #4a7c59);
        border-radius: 999px;
        height: 100%;
        min-height: 10rem;
        width: 0.36rem;
    }
    .copy {
        color: #304247;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .copy span {
        color: var(--maple);
        font-weight: 800;
    }
    .north-card {
        background: #102126;
        border-left: 0.35rem solid var(--maple);
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 55px rgba(16, 33, 38, 0.14);
        color: var(--snow);
        padding: 1.25rem;
    }
    .north-card strong {
        color: var(--ice);
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .north-card p {
        color: rgba(251, 251, 247, 0.84);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
    }
    @media (max-width: 820px) {
        .about-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 0.4rem 1fr;
        }
        .north-card {
            grid-column: 2;
        }
    }
</style>
